{"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.6","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.5","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.4"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Update your code to make use of the new state sharing tools in the library, such as the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Shared"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property wrapper, and the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"appStorage"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fileStorage"},{"text":" persistence strategies.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Composable Architecture is under constant development, and we are always looking for ways to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"simplify the library, and make it more powerful. This version of the library only introduced new"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"APIs and did not deprecate any existing APIs."}]},{"style":"important","type":"aside","name":"Important","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Before following this migration guide be sure you have fully migrated to the newest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"tools of version 1.9. See ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"},{"text":" for more information.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Sharing state","anchor":"Sharing-state"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The new tools added are concerned with allowing one to seamlessly share state with many parts of an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"application that is easy to understand, and most importantly, testable. See the dedicated","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/SharingState","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" article for more information on how to use these new tools.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To share state in one feature with another feature, simply use the "},{"code":"Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property wrapper:"}]},{"code":["@ObservableState","struct State {","  @Shared var signUpData: SignUpData","  \/\/ ...","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This will require that ","type":"text"},{"code":"SignUpData","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" be passed in from the parent, and any changes made to this state","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"will be instantly observed by all features holding onto it.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Further, there are persistence strategies one can employ in "},{"code":"@Shared","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". For example, if you want any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changes of "},{"code":"signUpData","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to be automatically persisted to the file system you can use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"fileStorage(_:decoder:encoder:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and specify a URL:"}]},{"code":["@ObservableState","struct State {","  @Shared(.fileStorage(URL(\/* ... *\/) var signUpData = SignUpData()","  \/\/ ...","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Upon app launch the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"signUpData"},{"type":"text","text":" will be populated from disk, and any changes made to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"signUpData"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will automatically be persisted to disk. Further, if the disk version changes, all instances of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"signUpData"},{"type":"text","text":" in the application will automatically update."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There is another persistence strategy for storing simple data types in user defaults, called"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":". It can refer to a value in user defaults by a string"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"key:"}]},{"code":["@ObservableState ","struct State {","  @Shared(.appStorage(\"isOn\")) var isOn = false","  \/\/ ...","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Similar to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fileStorage(_:decoder:encoder:)"},{"text":", upon launch of the application the initial","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"value of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isOn"},{"text":" will be populated from user defaults, and any change to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isOn"},{"text":" will be automatically","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"persisted to user defaults. Further, if the user defaults value changes, all instances of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isOn"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in the application will automatically update.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That is the basics of sharing data. Be sure to see the dedicated "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/SharingState","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" article"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for more detailed information."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.10"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"kind":"article","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Migrating to 1.10"},"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/MigratingTo1.9":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","kind":"article","abstract"